=You are a query parser. Extract:
- topic
- region
- timeframe and if no time specified return the current dont let timeframe be empty
from this text: {{$json.body.query}} 
Return JSON { "topic": "...", "region": "...", "timeframe": "..." }.   or if not return json  { "topic": "...", "region":"...", "timeframe": "..." }.    from   {{ $json.chatInput }}

